    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/ff35e072fbc480863c1b1546a4593bf0.poster.avif?t=1772143603\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/ff35e072fbc480863c1b1546a4593bf0.webm?t=1772143603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/ff35e072fbc480863c1b1546a4593bf0.mp4?t=1772143603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多3位朋友一起勇闯被诅咒的海域，为神秘的黑色舰队寻找禁忌宝藏。你能从潜伏在波涛之下的恐怖中生存下来吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/2dda2fe079eb7a77b320934e8577a65a.poster.avif?t=1772143603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/2dda2fe079eb7a77b320934e8577a65a.webm?t=1772143603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/2dda2fe079eb7a77b320934e8577a65a.mp4?t=1772143603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 在被诅咒的水域中规划航线，但要小心 - 这些岛屿隐藏着黑暗的秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 你的灯笼是黑暗中的生命线 - 明智地使用它，否则将面对潜伏在阴影中的饥饿之物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 与时间赛跑以获取古老的宝藏，如果你敢于深入探索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 感受队友的声音渐渐消失在远处时，恐惧逐渐蔓延</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 一起保持船只的漂浮，或成为被诅咒深渊中无数沉船的一部分</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/a99d5eb71a458527d8f51a967ba030c3.poster.avif?t=1772143603\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/a99d5eb71a458527d8f51a967ba030c3.webm?t=1772143603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/a99d5eb71a458527d8f51a967ba030c3.mp4?t=1772143603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这被诅咒的水域中，你的船是生存的唯一希望。但黑色舰队要求更多... 你会冒险深入，那里有无价的宝藏 - 以及难以言喻的恐怖在等待吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>潜伏的恐怖：</strong> 每一次吱嘎声，每一道阴影，黑暗中的每一丝低语都可能是你的最后警告</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>你的船：</strong> 在这被诅咒的水域中的唯一庇护所 - 保持它的完整，否则将面对深渊的恐怖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>古老的秘密：</strong> 从每次航行中生存下来，解锁更黑暗的水域和更大的奖励 - 如果你敢于回来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/bc0ff4d86b0b076c48fbcb38b628c16b.poster.avif?t=1772143603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/bc0ff4d86b0b076c48fbcb38b628c16b.webm?t=1772143603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022470/extras/bc0ff4d86b0b076c48fbcb38b628c16b.mp4?t=1772143603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的船员会团结一致对抗潜伏在下方的恐怖，还是黑暗的水域将再夺走一艘船？在这被诅咒的海域中，死亡仅仅是个开始。</p>",
